328
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] najradosniji se slavi.

329
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] A slavi se najradosniji jer je blizak

330
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] našim ljudskim iskustvima.

331
00:21:37,279 --> 00:21:39,180
[SPEAKER_00] Uskrs to me izmiče.

332
00:21:39,660 --> 00:21:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] Nije lako ući ovaj,

333
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:43,799
[SPEAKER_00] ali rekao bih to je neodvojivo.

334
00:21:43,799 --> 00:21:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] O tome sam govorio u prošloj emisiji

335
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] o kristovim otajstvima,

336
00:21:46,500 --> 00:21:49,400
