339
00:21:54,279 --> 00:21:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] vrhunac njegova života,

340
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] onoga što je on činio vrhunac,

341
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] očeva nauma o kristovu poslanju

342
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,700
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovu spasenju,

343
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] odkupljenju koje je vrši za nas,

344
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] je njegovo vazmeno otajstvo.

345
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, njegova muka, smrt

346
00:22:09,019 --> 00:22:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] i uskrsnuće.

347
00:22:09,859 --> 00:22:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] To je kruna njegova života.

348
00:22:11,579 --> 00:22:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] To je kruna njegova života.

349
00:22:13,759 --> 00:22:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] Sva su njegova otajstva,

350
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] kako je spovjedomo vjera,

351
00:22:17,099 --> 00:22:18,839
[SPEAKER_00] radi nas i našeg spasenja.

352
00:22:18,839 --> 00:22:20,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on je i uskrsnuo radi nas.

353
00:22:20,759 --> 00:22:22,240
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Pavel u prvoj koriničnjima,

354
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] 15. poglavlje,

355
00:22:23,099 --> 00:22:24,700
[SPEAKER_00] ako je Krist uskrsnuo,

356
00:22:24,700 --> 00:22:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] i mi ćemo uskrsnuti.

357
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] Postajući dijelovi njegova tijela,

358
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:31,259
[SPEAKER_00] crkve, koja je njegovo mistično tijelo,

359
00:22:31,259 --> 00:22:32,839
[SPEAKER_00] mi na neki način,

360
00:22:32,839 --> 00:22:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] evo, imamo jamstvo,

361
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:37,619
