366
00:22:42,559 --> 00:22:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] i mi očekujemo uskrsnuoće tijela

367
00:22:45,059 --> 00:22:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] i život vječni,

368
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:47,160
[SPEAKER_00] kako ispovjedamo

369
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] o pstovskom vjerovanju.

370
00:22:48,079 --> 00:22:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi nječima,

371
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kristova uskrsnuoće,

372
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] kao poruka,

373
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] da smrt ne ima zadnju riječ

