382
00:23:08,559 --> 00:23:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ja to radim?

383
00:23:09,819 --> 00:23:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] To će jednako nestati, propasti.

384
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:13,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nema uskrsnuoća,

385
00:23:14,660 --> 00:23:16,299
[SPEAKER_00] čemu živjeti?

386
00:23:16,299 --> 00:23:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto se truditi?

387
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:20,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako ima uskrsnuoća,

388
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] ako postoji život vječni,

389
00:23:21,779 --> 00:23:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] ako postoji mogućnost

390
