391
00:23:26,079 --> 00:23:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] a to je poruka uskrsnuoća,

392
00:23:28,099 --> 00:23:29,259
[SPEAKER_00] život ne nestaje,

393
00:23:29,259 --> 00:23:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] život se nastavlja

394
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,440
