397
00:23:34,559 --> 00:23:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako će tijelo?

398
00:23:35,599 --> 00:23:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

399
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bogu se moguće.

400
00:23:37,799 --> 00:23:40,240
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi nismo ljudi bez tijela.

401
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:42,000
