434
00:24:27,519 --> 00:24:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] sve to ostaje,

435
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:29,240
[SPEAKER_00] sve to ostaje.

436
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] Gradim, gradim,

437
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:31,480
