[SPEAKER_00] Božju državu.

441
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljestvo Božije.

442
00:24:39,279 --> 00:24:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to nas onda mora

