668
00:29:45,079 --> 00:29:46,240
[SPEAKER_00] donosi sve.

669
00:29:47,220 --> 00:29:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

670
00:29:47,519 --> 00:29:48,839
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovo rođenje je,

671
