685
00:30:15,819 --> 00:30:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da mi odrasli,

686
00:30:18,119 --> 00:30:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] roditelji i djeci,

687
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,640
[SPEAKER_00] mi svećenici drugima,

688
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] jedne drugima,

689
00:30:21,579 --> 00:30:24,359
