[SPEAKER_00] koje uvijek negdje vladaju

701
00:30:44,039 --> 00:30:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] i prijete svakom čovjeku

702
00:30:45,359 --> 00:30:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] i svakom ljudskom srcu.

703
00:30:46,319 --> 00:30:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz dobrotu.

704
00:30:48,559 --> 00:30:49,559
