708
00:30:53,279 --> 00:30:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] jer imamo običaj blagoslivnjanja hrane.

709
00:30:56,039 --> 00:30:57,319
[SPEAKER_01] Što stoji iza toga?

710
00:30:57,319 --> 00:30:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro,

711
