742
00:31:44,660 --> 00:31:47,180
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo ga rekonstruirati,

743
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo,

744
00:31:48,079 --> 00:31:49,259
[SPEAKER_00] možemo samo ponoviti,

745
00:31:49,259 --> 00:31:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] na temelju izjava svjedoka,

746
00:31:51,299 --> 00:31:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] povjerovati,

747
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] prihvatiti,

748
00:31:52,940 --> 00:31:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je on bio mrtav,

749
00:31:54,460 --> 00:31:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] i da je uskrsnuo.

750
00:31:56,119 --> 00:31:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je Krist doista uskrsnuo,

751
00:31:59,220 --> 00:31:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] a je,

752
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] to ima velike,

753
00:32:02,119 --> 00:32:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] za teologiju,

754
00:32:03,559 --> 00:32:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] to ima velike,

755
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] silne posljedice.

756
00:32:05,579 --> 00:32:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] Prva je,

757
00:32:06,539 --> 00:32:10,259
[SPEAKER_00] imali čovječanstvo,

758
00:32:10,259 --> 00:32:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] kao ukupnost,

759
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,819
[SPEAKER_00] evo, ljuskih života,

760
00:32:13,819 --> 00:32:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] ljuske povijesti,

761
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:16,259
[SPEAKER_00] imali neki smisao?

762
00:32:16,259 --> 00:32:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] postoji li,

763
00:32:19,059 --> 00:32:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] postoji li jedan cilj,

764
00:32:21,079 --> 00:32:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] kamo teče,

765
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] sav tijek povijesti?

766
00:32:23,319 --> 00:32:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je sve besmisleno?

767
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kristov,

768
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] u slučaju kaže,

769
00:32:28,019 --> 00:32:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] da,

770
00:32:28,279 --> 00:32:28,799
[SPEAKER_00] ima.

771
00:32:28,799 --> 00:32:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] Povijest nije,

772
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:32,200
[SPEAKER_00] cikliško ponavljanje,

773
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] u određenim periodima,

774
00:32:33,420 --> 00:32:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] ono što se već dogodilo,

775
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] tako da je,

776
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] propovedenje,

777
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,839
[SPEAKER_00] nema ništa novo poslunce,

778
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] nego je praktički,

779
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] cijela povijest ide,

780
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,720
[SPEAKER_00] jednoj točci,

781
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] a to je Kristov skrsli.

782
00:32:44,099 --> 00:32:48,160
[SPEAKER_00] Pava o tome jako dobro

783
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] u prvoj korinčanjima

784
00:32:49,140 --> 00:32:50,160
[SPEAKER_00] i knjiga otkrivenja.

785
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

786
00:32:50,740 --> 00:32:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] sve, sve,

787
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,779
[SPEAKER_00] mi to znali, ne znali,

788
00:32:53,779 --> 00:32:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] sve teži svoj nutarnji dinamizmom

789
00:32:56,119 --> 00:32:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji je Bog stavio u stvorenje,

790
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno, rekao bih,

791
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,140
[SPEAKER_00] u živote ljudi,

792
00:32:59,140 --> 00:33:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] sve ide jednoj točci,

793
00:33:00,819 --> 00:33:01,680
[SPEAKER_00] a to je,

794
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:04,140
[SPEAKER_00] da sve bude u Kristu

795
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] i Kristu svemu.

796
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kad on podloži, kaže,

797
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,660
[SPEAKER_00] sve pod Božje noge,

798
00:33:09,660 --> 00:33:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] tada će Krist biti sve u svemu,

799
00:33:11,279 --> 00:33:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] tada će biti dovršeno sve.

800
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:13,740
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo,

801
00:33:13,740 --> 00:33:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovu tijelu,

802
00:33:16,039 --> 00:33:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] uskrislom,

803
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo čovječanstvo,

804
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:20,400
[SPEAKER_00] da je dobilo svoj cilj

805
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:21,160
[SPEAKER_00] kamo teži,

806
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:21,819
[SPEAKER_00] a to je,

807
00:33:21,819 --> 00:33:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] on je točka omega,

808
00:33:23,619 --> 00:33:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] on je posljednji,

809
00:33:24,619 --> 00:33:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] on je završna točka cijela ljudičke povijesti,

810
00:33:26,759 --> 00:33:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego češta svemir.

811
00:33:28,019 --> 00:33:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] Svemir ima također

812
00:33:30,599 --> 00:33:31,799
[SPEAKER_00] svoj nutarnji dinamizam,

813
00:33:31,799 --> 00:33:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] tako ga je Bog stvorio,

814
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:36,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji teži jednoj točci.

815
00:33:37,039 --> 00:33:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] U Kristovu uskrisnuću

816
00:33:38,359 --> 00:33:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] materija je oduhovljena,

817
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:41,339
[SPEAKER_00] materija je preobražena,

818
00:33:41,339 --> 00:33:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] materija je došla do svog

819
00:33:43,539 --> 00:33:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] uzvišenja,

820
00:33:46,339 --> 00:33:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] do svog kraja.

821
00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je dodirila ono čemu teži,

822
00:33:49,339 --> 00:33:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] a to je proslava i materije.

823
00:33:52,259 --> 00:33:54,140
[SPEAKER_00] I Krist uskrislija onda

824
00:33:54,140 --> 00:33:56,180
[SPEAKER_00] i točka kamo čitavi svemir

825
00:33:56,180 --> 00:33:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] svojim nutarnjom dinamikom ide.

826
00:33:58,000 --> 00:34:01,660
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je usmjerno prema toj jednoj točci,

827
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:03,660
[SPEAKER_00] a to je Krist uskrisli i proslavljeni.

828
00:34:05,140 --> 00:34:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] on će praktički sve u njemu uzdignuto.

829
00:34:08,019 --> 00:34:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ovi blagoslovi o tome,

830
00:34:10,079 --> 00:34:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] maka ljudi tako ne razmišljaju,

831
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali o tome govore.

832
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kako njegovu uskrisnuće,

833
00:34:14,260 --> 00:34:16,800
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo ljudi kako su preobraženi,

834
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako su,

835
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] nego i materija.

836
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] Onda postaje blagoslova.

837
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] glagosivamo kao simbol te pobjede,

838
00:34:23,099 --> 00:34:24,179
[SPEAKER_00] tog preobraženja,

839
00:34:24,179 --> 00:34:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] tog dodirivanja,

840
00:34:25,699 --> 00:34:26,360
[SPEAKER_00] konačno.

841
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] U njegovu uskrisnuću imamo konačno,

842
00:34:28,579 --> 00:34:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja je ušla u povijest,

843
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali nam izmiče.

844
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno vjerim možemo to što nam možemo to prihvatiti

845
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] i onda prema tome usmjeri svoj život,

846
00:34:37,019 --> 00:34:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] prema tome težiti.

847
00:34:38,039 --> 00:34:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] Do mladene mi ovdje stavimo.

848
00:34:39,579 --> 00:34:41,400
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam na ovom ugodnom razgovoru.

849
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi gledate,

850
00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] evo pratite nas i dalje.

851
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mi vam iz portala Režarijeći želimo sretan uskrs.

852
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] S vama i vašima.

853
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:49,800
[SPEAKER_01] Boži blagoslov i vidimo se.

